title: (Software) Asterisk Key 8.3 Build 2976 - DLLOZ
description:
Description:

Asterisk Key reveals passwords that are hidden under asterisks. Unlike many others, this program works both with password dialog boxes and web page login forms. Asterisk Key shows your passwords hidden under asterisks. Asterisk Key is easy to use, just press a button, while the dialog or web page is open and it will detect and reveal all masked passwords.

More Info:

Asterisk is developed by Passware. It is compatible with all versions of Windows.
